    "Alternatively, they could be a group of individuals contracted by the ethics board (Fig. 1b) or by the company (Fig.",
    "There could also be more complex structures.",
    "For example, Meta's Oversight Board consists of two separate entities: a purpose trust 9 and a limited liability company (LLC) [130,165].",
